html:
All of the Service is paid for by your monthly fee. There are no third party revenue streams, no selling of advertising or personal data.

Title: MyKolab doesn't sell your personal data

Topic: personal-data

Summary: MyKolab's only source of revenue is the monthly fee paid by subscribers. This means that they don't sell advertising, which could place unwanted cookies and web beacons, nor do they sell your personal data.
